<figureCitation box="[881,969,1844,1870]" captionStart="FIGURE 24" captionStartId="16.[264,367,1331,1355]" captionTargetBox="[323,1268,300,1298]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[306,1282,283,1327]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURE 24. Known distribution of: Z. angustifasciatum; Z. batesi; Z. dugdalei; Z. kaikouraiensis; Z. minutum; Z. nonmaculatum; Z. taranakiensis; Z. opacum. The Z. batesi record on Kermadec Island is not shown here. (Map with permission from Ian Henderson, Massey University)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/170230/files/figure.png" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
